    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Creating a Guest User Record with Devise]]></title>
    <link href="http://shivamd.github.io/blog/2013/11/21/create-a-guest-user-record-with-devise/"/>
    <updated>2013-11-21T02:04:00+04:00</updated>
